Package com.intellij.openapi.roots.libraries

Class LibraryPresentationProvider<P extends LibraryProperties>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intellij.openapi.roots.libraries.LibraryPresentationProvider<P>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    GroovyLibraryPresentationProviderBase, LibraryType

    public abstract class LibraryPresentationProvider<P extends LibraryProperties>
extends java.lang.Object
    Implement this extension point to provide a custom icon and description for specific libraries in Project Structure dialog. Belonging to a specific kind is determined automatically by classes roots of a library using detect(List) method, if you need to specify it explicitly use LibraryType extension point instead.
    The implementation should be registered in plugin.xml: 
     <extensions defaultExtensionNs="com.intellij">
   <library.presentationProvider implementation="qualified-class-name"/>
 </extensions>
    See Also:
    LibraryType
